highlights.text: Bad Bunny has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “DÁKITI” is the highest at #1.
“Driving Home for Christmas” by Chris Rea is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 119 spots at #79.
“Shape of You” by Ed Sheeran has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 204 weeks straight.
“LA NOCHE DE ANOCHE” by Bad Bunny and ROSALÍA is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #2.
